'From Squeak2.6 of 11 October 1999 [latest update: #1613] on 19 November 1999 at 5:01:09 pm'!"Change Set:		UpdateAllBracesDate:			19 November 1999Author:			Dan IngallsThis changeSet causes all exissting brace constructs to be recompiled.That done it removes all the old methods that serviced them.Ready?  Here we go..."(Smalltalk allCallsOn: #fromBraceStack:) do:	[:str | MessageSet parse: str toClassAndSelector: 		[:cl :sel | cl recompile: sel from: cl]]!Collection removeSelector: #fill:fromStack:!ArrayedCollection removeSelector: #fill:fromStack:!ArrayedCollection class removeSelector: #fromBraceStack:!ContextPart removeSelector: #pop:toAddable:!ContextPart removeSelector: #pop:toIndexable:!